    <h1>Privacy Policy for DatabaseLearningTool</h1>

    <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> October 16, 2025</p>
    <p><strong>Last Updated:</strong> October 16, 2025</p>

    <p>This Privacy Policy governs the <strong>DatabaseLearningTool</strong> mobile application (the "App"), operated by <strong>stubborndeveloper</strong> (the "Developer").</p>

    <h2>1. No Collection of User Data</h2>
    <p>The <strong>DatabaseLearningTool</strong> App is designed to function entirely offline and does not require an internet connection, nor does it contain any features that track, collect, transmit, or store personal or sensitive user data.</p>
    <p>Specifically:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>We do not collect any Personal Data.</strong> This includes no names, email addresses, phone numbers, or any other personally identifiable information.</li>
        <li><strong>We do not collect Usage Data.</strong> This includes no device identifiers, IP addresses, crash logs, or analytics.</li>
        <li><strong>No Third-Party Access.</strong> The App does not contain any third-party analytics, advertisements, or external SDKs that could access or collect user data.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>2. No Data Sharing or Disclosure</h2>
    <p>Since we do not collect any data, we do not share, sell, or disclose any user data to any third parties.</p>

    <h2>3. Data Retention and Deletion</h2>
    <p>As we do not collect or store any user data, there is no data to retain or delete.</p>

    <h2>4. Security</h2>
    <p>While we take all reasonable steps to ensure the App is secure, since the App does not transmit or store any user data, there is no risk of remote data breach concerning your personal information through our service.</p>

    <h2>5. Developer and Contact Information</h2>
    <p>For any questions or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy or the App, please contact the developer, <strong>stubborndeveloper</strong>, at:</p>
    <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:alfrancisgabriel@gmail.com">alfrancisgabriel@gmail.com</a></p>

    <h2>6. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. The updated version will be indicated by a new "Last Updated" date and the revised policy will be posted on this page.</p>

